ass-scout.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"Scout Class from the Dead Planets Roblox Experience\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e25 C\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e• \u003cstrong\u003e50% faster\u003c/strong\u003e walking speed.\u003cbr/\u003e• \u003cstrong\u003eHighlight \u003c/strong\u003enearby enemies.\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+ \u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eBest early class.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+ \u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eHighest mobility.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+ \u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eExcellent utility.\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dead-planets-class-jetpacker.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"Jetpacker Class from the Dead Planets Roblox Experience\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e80 C\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e• A utility \u003cstrong\u003eJetpack \u003c/strong\u003ethat allows you to \u003cstrong\u003efly \u003c/strong\u003eshort distances.\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+ \u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eBest vertical mobility.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+ \u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eHigh utility.\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e– \u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eNo damage options.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/dead-planets-class-medic.png?resize=150%2C150\" alt=\"Medi Cl